==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}
# (''Geometry'') A [[solid]] discovered by C. J. Roberts of Baldock, England. It is constructed by slicing a 90-degree [[bicone]] through a [[plane]] containing both apexes, rotating one half by 90 degrees, and reconnecting them. The sphericon has a single continuous face, and two edges.

